org.osate.aadl2.modelsupport.errorreporting

Class QueuingAnalysisErrorReporter.Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osate.aadl2.modelsupport.errorreporting.QueuingAnalysisErrorReporter.Message
  • Enclosing class:
    QueuingAnalysisErrorReporter

    public static final class QueuingAnalysisErrorReporter.Message
extends java.lang.Object
    Record of a reported error message/warning. Contains the AObject on which the message is located, the category of the message, and the message itself. The category is a string, and the set of current values is given by QueuingAnalysisErrorReporter.ERROR, QueuingAnalysisErrorReporter.WARNING, and QueuingAnalysisErrorReporter.INFO.

    aarong
